cu.explanation_en: Setting the integrity algorithm to the unknown enum 'nia9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting dl_carrierBandwidth to 300 exceeds the maximum allowed value, causing configuration validation failure and preventing proper downlink setup.
du.explanation_zh: 將 dl_carrierBandwidth 設定為 300 超過最大允許值，會導致配置驗證失敗，並阻止正確的下行鏈路設置。
